Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:05.40,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yor's secret identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:06.82,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Briar Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.84,Default,Shopkeeper,0,0,0,,This time, you'll be protecting the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:12.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yor had been given one of her tallest orders yet:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.12,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}to protect the head of the mafia\Nfrom numerous assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.21,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.79,Default,Employee B,0,0,0,,We have a winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:20.98,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anya won first place in a raffle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:25.23,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Forgers all happened to \Nend up on the same cruise ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.51,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Many assassins had already snuck aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:34.68,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sickle-and-Chain Barnaby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.23,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? \NThe last thing I need is for this to escalate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.36,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,The lady from the circus is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.50,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice, Anya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:48.36,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anya did her best to make sure Loid \Ndidn't find out Yor's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:53.62,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was the most exciting\Nand valiant adventure yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:55.62,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Could you be any lamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:58.79,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yor was able to narrowly avoid \Nthe enemy's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.24,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:04.63,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}And during the fireworks show,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.01,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yor had to go head-to-head \Nagainst multiple assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:14.39,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I wanted was to protect his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.66,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I stand by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.26,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, I have more to lose than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:22.04,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure Loid would appreciate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:22.81,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:26.65,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:28.83,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:30.03,Default,opsync,0,0,0,,{opsync}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.65,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,The fireworks were so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.05,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.75,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,It's a shame that we couldn't find Yor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.51,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,The ship is just too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.77,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.28,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I totally forgot about Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.33,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to find her, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.57,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}The State Security officers seem uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.71,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.02,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Gather personnel quickly..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.54,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}"...has been set in a room..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.63,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bomb at the bottom of the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.47,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.64,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}But who set it? And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.29,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? Gather more information?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.66,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, the State Security \Nofficers will take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:06.98,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trying to intervene would be\Nextremely risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.15,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other hand, there are \Ncountless lives at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:13.48,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't just ignore this\Nconsidering the greater risk at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.09,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I also can't leave Anya alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.10,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:17.99,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.90,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna keep playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.92,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.70,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.50,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go play in there. \NYou go back to our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.37,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}A daycare center? Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:35.92,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,All right. I'll come get you in a bit, \Nthen. Just stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.76,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Okie dokie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.51,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Please take good care of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.58,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Her name is Anya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.88,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.39,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Wow, I get to play with a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.44,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, now's my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.39,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.90,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,What should we play with, Anya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:55.55,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I'm playing with this ball.{she will never be ballin....}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.93,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,You sure are. You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.67,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Gonna be bored with it soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.64,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,And I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.99,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Right, I guess that's enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.00,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna draw now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.91,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.24,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.92,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Okay, what would you like to draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.42,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.10,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Anya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.33,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,Well? Can you disarm it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:31.53,Default,State Security Service Officer A,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm trying to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:34.52,Default,State Security Service Officer C,0,0,0,,We're counting on you. There are some \Nreally important people on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.27,Default,State Security Service Officer A,0,0,0,,Just shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.52,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,I heard there was a bomb in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.68,Default,Crew,0,0,0,,Oh, it's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.55,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Pardon my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.55,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,I used to be in the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.34,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,It was my job to dismantle \Nand dispose of explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:51.04,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,I'd like to offer my assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.45,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Is it possible to move it away from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.99,Default,State Security Service Officer A,0,0,0,,You can't. It's rigged to blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:02.46,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,A time bomb, type B-CP62.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.17,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bomb that extremists \Nfrom the West love using.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.17,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Were they after a high-profile Eastern official?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.92,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or the ship as a whole?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:12.36,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, HQ would've told me about any\Nongoing extremist operations.{No, I haven't heard anything from \NHQ about a group like that.}{K: imo "western operations" makes it sound like the extremists are part of the government, but to me it sounds like those extremist/terrorist groups are separate from the government}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.56,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's possible the bomb was designed\Nto look like the West was responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.28,Default,State Security Service Officer A,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.57,Default,State Security Service Officer A,0,0,0,,Think you can deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.94,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.42,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll help Mommy while he's dealing with the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.32,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:33.21,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think she slaughtered \Nall those well-known assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.83,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a terrifying woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.97,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a bad guy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.84,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's definitely time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.80,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've made more than enough from this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.09,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm getting the hell outta here \Nbefore the hyenas start circling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:50.60,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}You guys can keep squabbling \Nfor what time you have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.60,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}The front of the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:56.14,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon enough, this whole ship will be underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.90,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}And they'll all be clueless\Nuntil it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.25,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost the bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.90,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter. Now, \NI need to focus on finding Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.91,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}The roof toward the front! \NThe roof toward the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.63,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's... Mommy's stabby thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.58,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.85,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't get close enough \Nto him to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.20,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mommy's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.30,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's fighting without her stabby thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.11,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't hear her from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.67,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to climb up somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.12,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.95,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1} I gotta save Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.59,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Reach her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:08.01,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Rising Hope!{what}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.79,Default,Tank Top,0,0,0,,Quit making all that noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:24.86,Default,Sunglasses,0,0,0,,It wasn't me! I dunno what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.73,Default,Tank Top,0,0,0,,If that nutcase finds us, we're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.28,Default,Sunglasses,0,0,0,,You think I don't know that?\NWe gotta strike now while she's distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.29,Default,Sunglasses,0,0,0,,Gretcher is completely defenseless right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.83,Default,Grey,0,0,0,,How much longer do you think\Nwe'll be down here? {K: slightly vague? consider "We're not stuck here forever, are we?" or similar}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.92,Default,Sunglasses,0,0,0,,Once we kill them, \Nwe're getting the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.79,Default,Sunglasses,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.10,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exactly as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.07,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gunshots from behind?!{c: backshots, if you will}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.90,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's my—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.09,Default,Katana Guy,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:29.67,Default,Katana Guy,0,0,0,,I'm going to end this with my next strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:42.06,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're done for. \NYou've left yourself completely open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.15,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.04,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to Mommy's battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:26.95,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's finally over... I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.45,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}She won! And she couldn't have done it without me. {K: this is fine, though consider rewording it to something with more of an "it's all thanks to me" nuance}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.74,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I need to let Olka and the others out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.15,Default,State Security Service Officer C,0,0,0,,He successfully disarmed it!
Comment: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:48.82,Alt,State Security Service Officer C,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:48.82,Default,State Security Service Officers,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.97,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.19,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm far more nervous about\Nbeing surrounded by so many
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.51,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}State Security officers than the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:58.98,Default,State Security Service Officer C,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.10,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,Farewell, {\i1}Princess Lorelei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:10.76,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,It'll be nice listening to their cries\Nas I drift away.{Let me hear all the screams of \Nagony as you sink to your doom.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:28.38,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,But where did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.34,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was someone trying to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:35.05,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! I must withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:41.55,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:45.44,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Director! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.27,Default,State Security Service Officer A,0,0,0,,There are still multiple bombs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:55.12,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,If the suspect's goal is to sink this ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.94,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,the amount of gunpowder here \Nis nowhere near enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.53,Default,State Security Service Officer C,0,0,0,,We should call for an evacuation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.58,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,To where, exactly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.29,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,We don't even know how many bombs \Nthere are or where they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.79,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,Besides, the guest list is full \Nof important people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.54,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,We can't cause a commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.77,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're trying to save face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:14.22,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,You know what'll happen if \Nyou blab any of this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:18.26,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,Gather available men\Nto search the rest of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.55,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,That goes for the crew, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.77,Default,State Security Service Officer B,0,0,0,,Don't let the higher-ups figure \Nout what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:33.37,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to hurry back before \Nthe caretaker gets suspicious!{or "notices" or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:39.64,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}This hurts so fucking bad! \NI need to get this thing out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:43.05,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't fight in this state.\NI've got to figure out a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.58,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not stopping 'til they're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.27,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,A bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.58,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,What'd you just say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.84,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.59,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}a bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.44,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a bomb inside the clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.35,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that wasn't the only bomb\Nthat Daddy had to deal with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.84,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:10.88,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:15.13,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! I need to tell Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.65,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't know where he is anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:21.66,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I was able to tell him,\Nhe'd figure out my secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.91,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,{\i1}How am I supposed to find a bomb around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:28.98,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,{\i1}They told me to search the lower decks,\Nbut that's so vague it's practically useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.66,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:33.67,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,Huh? Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:37.43,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Earlier, I saw a weird old guy stick a bom—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:40.02,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,a boogie onto that clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.93,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,That's real gross, so please clean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:46.46,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,A booger? Sorry miss, but I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:47.55,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:52.17,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, information about some weirdo\Nis exactly what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.69,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, it's not very likely, \Nbut I guess it couldn't hurt to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.00,Default,Crew A,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.78,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:04.38,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{\an8}Those fireworks were amazing, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.66,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pardon me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.12,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tomorrow, we'll be on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.96,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hear 'em loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.89,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't push yourself too much, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:17.46,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sounds like the bodyguard won.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.48,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec' there, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.72,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're \Ngoing all by your lonesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.42,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,Great to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.86,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,You're the one who planted \Nthe bombs, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.66,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,You were planning to take \Nall of us out with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.94,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,Yeah, and what are you going to do about it? {K: note, this is "loser" as in he's literally dissing him for losing the fight against yor}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.90,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,This is the perfect opportunity to kill\Nall targets in one fell swoop. {K: our targets = lit. "our targets, and Garden". consider either specifying Garden or rewording to "all of our targets"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.93,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,I told you some of the client's \Nguests were on that ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:49.12,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,Not like any of them are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:53.50,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The bombs are made to \Nlook like they were made in the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:58.78,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,If things go well, war will break out again, \Nand weapon sales will be through the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.88,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,The client will be plenty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.48,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.88,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Get this boat moving. We're starting from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.35,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,Who the hell said I'd give you a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:11.39,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,There's only enough food and water for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:15.77,Default,Glasses,0,0,0,,Is that right? I guess I won't be sharing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.69,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,Bombs have been located \Nin the third cargo room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.65,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,the upper part of the balance tank,\N and the boiler room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.49,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Right. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.11,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,From what you're describing, it sounds like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.59,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,all the bombs were \Nplanted by the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.41,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Please be careful of the trap\N I mentioned and proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.42,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Okay, on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.83,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.42,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,The upper floors... on the eighth deck, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.71,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.98,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}With all these people around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.32,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their goal isn't just to sink the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.88,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,We're just doing some \Nmaintenance on the clock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.21,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,We need to get these people away—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.56,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. There's probably no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:15:59.94,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.80,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,We're just conducting some inspections!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.87,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,Uh, hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.93,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,I'm going to go throw this into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.07,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:19.20,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to a little performance\Nbefore I off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.60,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,We're about to witness the goriest\Nfirework show of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:26.06,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,You'll be able to enjoy \Nthe symphony of agonized screams
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.34,Default,Informant,0,0,0,,from the wiretaps throughout the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:34.35,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Wait! That clock is an antique!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.76,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Whew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.37,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Hm? Was there something down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.48,Default,Guest A,0,0,0,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.16,Default,Guest B,0,0,0,,More fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.77,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Could you make some kind of \Nannouncement so there's no commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.38,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.38,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:05.63,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}He saved the day! \NWhich he couldn't have done without me.{K: same comment as 10:30, but also optional}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.13,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.04,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,How dare you wander off like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.46,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.52,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I-It's because I was about \Nto poop my pants...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.53,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Then you should've just said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.53,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,We're heading back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.28,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Wait! There are still bombs we haven't dealt with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.18,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't you just say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.15,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Let's head to the bathroom, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.79,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Thoroughly inspect each section, \Nincluding the upper floors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.47,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,It's possible there are still\Nterrorists on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:36.91,Default,Disguised Loid,0,0,0,,Please request that State Security \N be on guard around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.91,Default,Crew B,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:48.23,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I thought I just heard some faint explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.44,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Some of them may still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.93,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Stay on your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.63,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,All right. We're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.68,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, but let's lower the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:01.64,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Until the cruise ship gets far enough, \Nplease stay covered with this cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.44,Default,Grey,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.44,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.95,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,Thank you... so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:20.19,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Wait, your clothes are going to \Nget dirty! There's blood—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.71,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,He wants a hug goodbye, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.71,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, I really shouldn't. My hands are quite dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:35.09,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,Those hands are the reason\Nhe has a future to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:47.14,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,He's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:52.74,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,{\i1}This might be naïve of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:55.82,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,{\i1}and maybe I should mind my own business,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.91,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,{\i1}but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:03.71,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,{\i1}I pray that you find true peace \Nand harmony with your family.
Comment: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.71,Default,Olka,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be able to find true peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:07.50,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,It seems like the coast is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.29,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Now we just have to wait for \Nword from the retrieval ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.14,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Remain vigilant until the dawn breaks—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.93,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Stop letting yourself become sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:27.82,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Remember that we are nothing \Nmore than foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.60,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.53,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.61,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,I forgot I had a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:39.67,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Forger wants to make plans\Nfor the resort tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.67,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,on the island we'll be staying at.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.04,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Loid and Anya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:43.44,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Oh, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.00,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,I'll be on the lookout for any stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:49.52,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,As a reward for completing this \Nmission, see their request through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.50,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Make sure you ice your face so \Nthey don't see the swelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.30,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.00,Default,Matthew,0,0,0,,don't let them see what happened\Nto your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:03.21,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:05.16,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'll wear something that covers it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:10.74,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miraculously, I was able to \Nensure everyone's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:14.32,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I can leave the rest \Nto the State Security Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.82,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.51,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,I guess she got tuckered out from waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.58,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:30.55,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it was an emergency, but I ended \Nup casting my family aside again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.84,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you even saying, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.54,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your "family" is a part of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:40.36,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, my mission was supposed to be the vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.60,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I guess I wasn't supposed to... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:00.05,Default,edsync,0,0,0,,{edsync}
